en_58093_0	A team of professionals in the Badulla Disaster Management Centre (DMC), held an awareness workshop on ‘Disaster Management’ for troops of the Security Force Headquarters - Central (SFHQ-Cen) on Friday (14) at the request of Major General Rukmal Dias, Commander, Security Forces - Central (SF-Cen).
en_58093_1	The full-day workshop, attended by more than 20 Army personnel learnt on recommended and laid down guidelines and practices in emergencies, ahead of the forthcoming rainy season.
en_58093_2	Director (preparedness) at DMC, Uva Province, Mr Sunil Jayaweera and DMC Assistant Director, Uva Province, Mr Udaya Kumara were also present during this programme.
